The paper discusses a neural network system that uses external knowledge to improve the inference process. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The system also uses fuzzy cognitive maps (FCMs), which are a type of neural network, indicating the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses a learning algorithm to improve network performance, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses a stop condition to prevent the learning algorithm from iterating without decreasing the simulation error, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
